    <statement><p>Solve the quadratic equation</p>
<p><me>8(x+1)^2 - 3(x+1)^4 + 5 = 0\text{.}</me></p>
<p>Give your answer to at least three decimal places.</p>
<p>Smaller solution: <fillin characters="10" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
<p>Larger solution: <fillin characters="10" name="AnSwEr0002"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>-2.78585</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <answer>
